Choose from a variety of exquisite options to enhance your everyday meals and gatherings. Whether you're looking for the perfect gift set or standalone pieces to keep your food and beverages at the ideal temperature, Arizona H-7 has you covered.

Variations:

5 Pcs Gift Pack Glass Top: This comprehensive set includes a cooler and a range of hotpots in small, medium, and large sizes, along with a reliable thermos to keep your beverages just the way you like them.

4 Pcs Gift Pack Glass Top: Perfect for smaller gatherings, this set features a cooler and hotpots in small, medium, and large sizes - everything you need to keep your dishes piping hot or refreshingly cool.

3 Pcs Set Glass Top: A trio of hotpots in small, medium, and large sizes, ideal for those who desire the convenience of versatile and efficient serving options.

Cooler 14 liter: The 14-liter cooler is designed to keep your beverages icy cold, ensuring you can enjoy refreshing drinks no matter the weather.

Small Hotpot: A compact and stylish hotpot to keep your favorite dishes warm and ready to serve.

Medium Hotpot: An intermediate-sized hotpot, perfect for serving mid-sized meals with flair.

Large Hotpot: The grand hotpot, designed for serving large meals with sophistication and precision.

Elevate your dining experience with the stylish and functional Danny Home 2-Tier Platter Perfect for serving appetizers, desserts, or fruits, this elegant set adds a sophisticated touch to any table setting. The tiered design allows you to display a variety of treats in an organized, space-saving manner, making it ideal for entertaining guests or enhancing your daily meals.

Crafted from high-quality materials, this durable and easy-to-clean platter set is both practical and beautiful. The sleek tier stand provides a sturdy foundation, while the smooth, spacious platters ensure your items are displayed to perfection. Whether you're hosting a party, enjoying an afternoon tea, or simply arranging your favorite snacks, this versatile 2-tier platter with tier stand is a must-have for any home.

  • Durable: Made from high-quality materials for long-lasting use.

  • Space-Saving: Maximizes serving space while keeping your treats organized.

  • Easy to Clean: Simple to wipe down and maintain.

Perfect for any occasion, the Danny Home 2-Tier Platter is the ideal choice for those looking to impress guests or enjoy a beautifully presented spread at home.

About this item

  • 【Stovetop Safe】Our glass teapot are made of borosilicate lead-free glass, free of any metals and toxins. The glass tea kettle for stovetop can withstand temperatures from -68°F to 302°F, so the glass tea pot can be placed directly on stove top or electric stove. The glass tea kettle with infuser is stovetop-safe, microwave-safe and dishwasher-safe.
  • 【Tight Sealing Bamboo Lid】The glass teapot for stovetop comes with a tight silicone reinforced bamboo lid, ensuring it is 100% airtight and leak-proof. So you can enjoy your tea easily without the boiling hot liquid leaking or spilling when you turn the glass tea kettle.
  • 【Removable Filter Spout】This glass teapot with infuser has a removable infuser. This infuser is made of 18/8 stainless steel that can filter most teas. You can use this glass tea pot to brew loose leaf tea, tea bags, blooming camellia, fruit tea, herbal tea.
  • 【Multiple functions】The glass teapot for stovetop has a capacity of 34 OZ, allowing you to prepare a variety of different beverages, teas, coffees as needed, allowing you to enjoy tea time with family and friends at any social gathering!
  • 【Wonderful Gift Ideal】The glass tea kettle for stovetop comes with beautiful gift boxes which is a perfect gift for family and friends! (such as Mother's Day, Father's Day, Thanksgiving, Christmas, Thanksgiving).
  • 【Easy to Clean】The glass teapot with infuser features a wide mouth design, which allows you to reach directly into the glass tea kettle and wash it by hand. All parts of the glass tea pot are dishwasher safe, making making tea a breeze. But in order to reduce the collision of the glass teapot in the dishwasher, please try not to wash it in the dishwasher.
